<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">
  <Import Project="$(EndjinProjectPropsPath)" Condition="$(EndjinProjectPropsPath) != ''" />
  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>net10.0</TargetFramework>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <LangVersion>preview</LangVersion>
    <TreatWarningsAsErrors>true</TreatWarningsAsErrors>
    <WarningsNotAsErrors>$(WarningsNotAsErrors);NU1901;NU1902;NU1903;NU1904</WarningsNotAsErrors>
    <!-- The AsyncAPI-generated CTJ model code (Generated/Models) carries XML-doc param tags that do not match the
         emitted signatures; Endjin TreatWarningsAsErrors would otherwise promote them. Same set as the other codegen
         projects. -->
    <NoWarn>$(NoWarn);CS1591;NU1504;CS1572;CS1573;CS1574;CS1584;CS1658</NoWarn>
    <EndjinDisableCreateEditorConfig>true</EndjinDisableCreateEditorConfig>
    <IsPackable>true</IsPackable>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>Apache-2.0</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <Description>The control-plane system workflows (design §16.5.1): the bootstrapped access-approval workflow specs and the generated AsyncAPI producer/consumer for its access.decision exchange, so the control plane can publish an approver's decision (PublishAccessDecisionProducer) and a system runner can consume it (ReceiveAccessDecisionConsumer) to resume the suspended approval run. Transport-agnostic (depends only on the IMessageTransport abstraction). Regenerate the messaging with the Corvus.Json.Cli asyncapi-generate command over specs/access-approval.asyncapi.json (rootNamespace Corvus.Text.Json.Arazzo.Durability.ControlPlane.SystemWorkflows, outputPath Generated, mode both).</Description>
  </PropertyGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <ProjectReference Include="..\Corvus.Text.Json\Corvus.Text.Json.csproj" />
    <ProjectReference Include="..\Corvus.Text.Json.AsyncApi\Corvus.Text.Json.AsyncApi.csproj" />
    <ProjectReference Include="..\Corvus.Text.Json.Arazzo.Durability\Corvus.Text.Json.Arazzo.Durability.csproj" />
  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="Endjin.RecommendedPractices.GitHub" PrivateAssets="All" />
    <PackageReference Include="StyleCop.Analyzers" PrivateAssets="All" />
    <PackageReference Include="Roslynator.Analyzers" PrivateAssets="All" />
  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="specs\**\*.json" />
  </ItemGroup>
</Project>
